itools 0.62.7 (2011/02/17)
==========================

itools is a Python library, it groups a number of packages into a single
meta-package for easier development and deployment:

  itools.abnf             itools.i18n             itools.rss
  itools.core             itools.ical             itools.srx
  itools.csv              itools.log              itools.stl
  itools.database         itools.loop             itools.tmx
  itools.datatypes        itools.odf              itools.uri
  itools.fs               itools.office           itools.web
  itools.gettext          itools.pdf              itools.workflow
  itools.git              itools.pkg              itools.xliff
  itools.handlers         itools.python           itools.xml
  itools.html             itools.relaxng          itools.xmlfile
  itools.http             itools.rest

This release has some minor features and bug fixes.

itools.database:
- new utility function 'pprint_query'
- now the 'get_revisions' method can filter by author and message
- fix the default values in the 'get_handler_class' method

itools.datatypes:
- fix 'enumerate_get_namespace' when value is a Path object

itools.handlers:
- fix the 'checkid' function for some cases

itools.web:
- define the expiration time of the authenticatation cookie in the
  server class, change the default back to 0 (does not expire)
- fix 'Context.del_cookie' for some browsers, like Firefox 4 (#1155)

Other:
- documentation, update the ODF chapter
- update the French translation


